<lb n="0032a21" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0032a2101">制<app type="star" corresp="#0031026"><lem wit="【大】">多</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】">吒</rdg></app>迦童子真言曰<note place="inline">外<note n="0032005" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔縛〕－【甲】【乙】</note><note n="0032005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">縛【大】，〔－〕【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0032005"><lem wit="【大】">縛</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>五<note n="0032006" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">股＝𦙶【甲】，鈷【乙】</note><note n="0032006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">股【大】，𦙶【甲】，鈷【乙】</note><app n="0032006"><lem wit="【大】">股</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">𦙶</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">鈷</rdg></app>印</note>。</p>
