<lb n="0032a26" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0032a2601">次本尊真言曰<note place="inline">通用經中印</note>。
<lb n="0032a27" ed="T"/><cb:tt><cb:t xml:lang="sa-Sidd"><g ref="#SD-DA42"/></cb:t><cb:t xml:lang="zh-Hant">唵<note n="0032009" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔一〕－【乙】</note><note n="0032009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">一【大】，〔－〕【乙】</note><app n="0032009"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">一</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app></cb:t></cb:tt><cb:tt><cb:t xml:lang="sa-Sidd"><g ref="#SD-CFC5"/></cb:t><cb:t xml:lang="zh-Hant">阿</cb:t></cb:tt><cb:tt><cb:t xml:lang="sa-Sidd"><g ref="#SD-A47C"/></cb:t><cb:t xml:lang="zh-Hant">左</cb:t></cb:tt><cb:tt><cb:t xml:lang="sa-Sidd"><g ref="#SD-A64A"/></cb:t><cb:t xml:lang="zh-Hant"><app type="star" corresp="#0031032"><lem wit="【大】">囉</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">羅</rdg></app><app type="star" corresp="#0032007"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">二</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app></cb:t></cb:tt><cb:tt><cb:t xml:lang="sa-Sidd"><g ref="#SD-A47C"/></cb:t><cb:t xml:lang="zh-Hant">贊</cb:t></cb:tt><cb:tt><cb:t xml:lang="sa-Sidd"><g ref="#SD-C9FD"/></cb:t><cb:t xml:lang="zh-Hant">拏<note place="inline">三</note></cb:t></cb:tt><cb:tt><cb:t xml:lang="sa-Sidd"><g ref="#SD-E045"/></cb:t><cb:t xml:lang="zh-Hant">唅<note n="0032010" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">所歸本尊四字乙本作本文</note><note n="0032010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">(所歸本尊)【大】，所敬本尊【乙】</note><app n="0032010"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">所<note n="0032011" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">歸＝敬【甲】【乙】</note><note n="0032011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">歸【大】，敬【甲】</note><app n="0032011"><lem wit="【大】">歸</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">敬</rdg></app>本尊</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">所敬本尊</rdg></app></cb:t></cb:tt></p>
<lb n="0032a28" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0032a29" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0032a2901">次說像法。</p>
<pb n="0032b" xml:id="T21.1204.0032b" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0032b01" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0032b0101">行者點取一清<note n="0032012" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔淨〕－【乙】</note><note n="0032012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">淨【大】，〔－〕【乙】</note><app n="0032012"><lem wit="【大】">淨</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>靜處。勿令見人及與非人。
<lb n="0032b02" ed="T"/>即行者與工人共清淨著新淨<note n="0032b0201" resp="CBETA" type="add">衣【CB】，依【大】</note><app n="0032b0201"><lem wit="【CB】" resp="CBETA.maha">衣<note type="cf1">T01n0008_p0211a13</note><note type="cf2">T03n0159_p0304a16</note></lem><rdg wit="【大】">依</rdg></app>。取白㲲或
<lb n="0032b03" ed="T"/>淨<note n="0032013" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">版＝板【甲】【乙】</note><note n="0032013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">版【大】，板【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0032013"><lem wit="【大】">版</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】">板</rdg></app>或淨衣。令畫本尊與八<note n="0032014" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔大〕－【乙】</note><note n="0032014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">大【大】，〔－〕【乙】</note><app n="0032014"><lem wit="【大】">大</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>童子<note n="0032015" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">本尊乃至像七字乙本作本文</note><note n="0032015" resp="CBETA" type="mod">(本尊通用經中像)【大】，本尊通用經中像【乙】</note><app n="0032015"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">本尊通用經中
<lb n="0032b04" ed="T"/>像</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">本尊通用經中像</rdg></app>。</p>
<lb n="0032b05" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0032b0501">慧光之形。少忿怒著天冠。身白黃色。右手持
<lb n="0032b06" ed="T"/>五智杵。左手蓮上置<note n="0032016" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">月＝日【甲】【乙】</note><note n="0032016" resp="CBETA" type="mod">月【大】，日【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0032016"><lem wit="【大】">月</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】">日</rdg></app>輪。袈裟瓔珞種種莊
<lb n="0032b07" ed="T"/>嚴。</p>
<lb n="0032b08" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0032b0801">次慧喜菩薩。形似慈面現微笑相。色如紅蓮。
<lb n="0032b09" ed="T"/>左手持摩尼。右手持三<note n="0032017" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">股＝釵【甲】【乙】</note><note n="0032017" resp="CBETA" type="mod">股【大】，釵【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0032017"><lem wit="【大】">股</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】">釵</rdg></app>鉤。</p>
<lb n="0032b10" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0032b1001">阿耨達菩薩形如梵王。色如真金頂戴金翅
<lb n="0032b11" ed="T"/>鳥。左手執蓮華。右手持獨<note n="0032018" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">股＝鈷【甲】【乙】＊</note><note n="0032018" resp="CBETA" type="mod">股【大】＊，鈷【甲】【乙】＊</note><app n="0032018"><lem wit="【大】">股</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】">鈷</rdg></app>杵。而乘龍王。</p>
<lb n="0032b12" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0032b1201">指德菩薩形如夜叉。色如虛空而有<note n="0032019" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔三目…手〕十一字－【甲】</note><note n="0032019" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（三目…手）十一字【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app cb:word-count="11" n="0032019"><lem wit="【大】">三目著
<lb n="0032b13" ed="T"/><note n="0032020" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">甲冑＝鏎鏪【乙】</note><note n="0032020" resp="CBETA" type="mod">甲冑【大】，鏎鏪【乙】</note><app n="0032020"><lem wit="【大】">甲冑</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">鏎鏪</rdg></app>。左手持<note n="0032021" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">輪＝錀【乙】</note><note n="0032021" resp="CBETA" type="mod">輪【大】，錀【乙】</note><app n="0032021"><lem wit="【大】">輪</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">錀</rdg></app>。右手</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>三<note n="0032022" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">叉＝釵【甲】【乙】</note><note n="0032022" resp="CBETA" type="mod">叉【大】，釵【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0032022"><lem wit="【大】">叉</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】">釵</rdg></app>鉾。</p>
<lb n="0032b14" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0032b1401">烏俱婆誐戴五<app type="star" corresp="#0032018"><lem wit="【大】">股</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】">鈷</rdg></app>冠。現暴惡相身如金色。
<lb n="0032b15" ed="T"/><note n="0032023" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">右＝左【甲】，【乙】＊</note><note n="0032023" resp="CBETA" type="mod">右【大】，左【甲】，【乙】＊</note><app n="0032023"><lem wit="【大】">右</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】">左</rdg></app>手執<app type="star" corresp="#0031033"><lem wit="【大】">縛</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">嚩</rdg></app>日<app type="star" corresp="#0031032"><lem wit="【大】">囉</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">羅</rdg></app>。<note n="0032024" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">左＝右【甲】，【乙】＊</note><note n="0032024" resp="CBETA" type="mod">左【大】，右【甲】，【乙】＊</note><app n="0032024"><lem wit="【大】">左</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】">右</rdg></app>手作拳印。</p>
<lb n="0032b16" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0032b1601">清淨比丘剃除首<note n="0032025" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">髮＝髻【乙】</note><note n="0032025" resp="CBETA" type="mod">髮【大】，髻【乙】</note><app n="0032025"><lem wit="【大】">髮</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">髻</rdg></app>。而著法袈裟。於<app type="star" corresp="#0032024"><lem wit="【大】">左</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">右</rdg></app>肩
<lb n="0032b17" ed="T"/>結垂。左手執梵<note n="0032026" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">夾＝天【乙】</note><note n="0032026" resp="CBETA" type="mod">夾【大】，天【乙】</note><app n="0032026"><lem wit="【大】">夾</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">天</rdg></app>。右手當心持五<app type="star" corresp="#0032018"><lem wit="【大】">股</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】">鈷</rdg></app>杵。
<lb n="0032b18" ed="T"/><app type="star" corresp="#0032023"><lem wit="【大】">右</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">左</rdg></app>肩現露。於腰纏赤裳。其面貌非若非老。
<lb n="0032b19" ed="T"/>目如青蓮。其口上牙於下顯出。</p>
<lb n="0032b20" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0032b2001">次矜羯<app type="star" corresp="#0031032"><lem wit="【大】">囉</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">羅</rdg></app>形如十五歲童。著蓮華冠身白肉
<lb n="0032b21" ed="T"/>色。二手合掌。其二大指與頭指間。橫<note n="0032027" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔插〕－【乙】</note><note n="0032027" resp="CBETA" type="mod">插【大】，〔－〕【乙】</note><app n="0032027"><lem wit="【大】">插</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>一
<lb n="0032b22" ed="T"/><note n="0032028" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">股＝鈷【甲】，枯【乙】</note><note n="0032028" resp="CBETA" type="mod">股【大】，鈷【甲】，<!--CBETA todo type: newmod-->枯【乙】</note><app n="0032028"><lem wit="【大】">股</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】">鈷</rdg></app>杵。天衣袈裟微妙嚴飾。</p>
<lb n="0032b23" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0032b2301">次制吒迦亦如童子。色如紅蓮頭結五髻
<lb n="0032b24" ed="T"/><note n="0032029" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">一結乃至五智十二字乙本作本文</note><note n="0032029" resp="CBETA" type="mod">(一結頂上之中一結額上二結頭左右一結頂後表五方五智)【大】，一結頂上之中一結額上二結頭左右一結頂後表五方五智【乙】</note><app n="0032029"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">一結頂上之中。<note n="0032030" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔一結額上〕－【甲】【乙】</note><note n="0032030" resp="CBETA" type="mod">一結額上【大】，〔－〕【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0032030"><lem wit="【大】">一結額上</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>。二結頭左右。<note n="0032031" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔一結〕－【甲】【乙】</note><note n="0032031" resp="CBETA" type="mod">一結【大】，〔－〕【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0032031"><lem wit="【大】">一結</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>頂後。表五方五智</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">一結頂上之中一結額上二結頭左右一結頂後表五方五智</rdg></app>左手嚩日囉。
<lb n="0032b25" ed="T"/>右手執金剛棒。<note n="0032032" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">瞋心＝順【甲】【乙】</note><note n="0032032" resp="CBETA" type="mod">瞋心【大】，順【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0032032"><lem wit="【大】">瞋心</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】">順</rdg></app>惡性之者故不著袈裟。
<lb n="0032b26" ed="T"/><note n="0032033" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（然）＋以【甲】，以＝然似【乙】</note><note n="0032033" resp="CBETA" type="mod">以【大】，然以【甲】，然似【乙】</note><app n="0032033"><lem wit="【大】">以</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">然以</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">然似</rdg></app>天衣纏其頸肩。畫像法說已竟。</p>
<lb n="0032b27" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0032b2701">次說供養法。</p>
<lb n="0032b28" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0032b2801">行者欲陳供養者。先須發菩提心。云何菩提
<lb n="0032b29" ed="T"/>心。謂發救眾生之心。思惟眾生苦惱起拔濟
<pb n="0032c" xml:id="T21.1204.0032c" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0032c01" ed="T"/>心也。如是發心時。不動明王及八大童子為
<lb n="0032c02" ed="T"/>不請師。從自心出護持行者。應當供養。住於
<lb n="0032c03" ed="T"/>山林寂靜之處。燒香散花持念真言。如是行
<lb n="0032c04" ed="T"/>時。使者現身隨意奉仕。先須禮四方如來發
<lb n="0032c05" ed="T"/>大誓願。</p>
<lb n="0032c06" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0032c0601">即禮東方作是念言。眾生無邊誓願度。是大
<lb n="0032c07" ed="T"/>圓鏡智<note n="0032034" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">願＝因【甲】</note><note n="0032034" resp="CBETA" type="mod">願【大】，因【甲】</note><app n="0032034"><lem wit="【大】">願</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">因</rdg></app>也。即菩提心門。菩提心即度眾生
<lb n="0032c08" ed="T"/>心。故發此願作禮者。乃至成佛常得金剛薩
<lb n="0032c09" ed="T"/>埵加持。令菩提心圓滿。</p>
<lb n="0032c10" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0032c1001">次禮南方作是念言。福智無邊誓願集。是平
<lb n="0032c11" ed="T"/>等性智之因也。即福智門。以福智二種資糧
<lb n="0032c12" ed="T"/>利益眾生故。若發此願作此禮者。乃至成佛
<lb n="0032c13" ed="T"/>地地中常得虛空藏<note n="0032035" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔菩薩〕－【乙】</note><note n="0032035" resp="CBETA" type="mod">菩薩【大】，〔－〕【乙】</note><app n="0032035"><lem wit="【大】">菩薩</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>授與灌頂。福智圓
<lb n="0032c14" ed="T"/>滿。</p>
<lb n="0032c15" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0032c1501">次禮西<note n="0032036" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">方＋（而）【乙】</note><note n="0032036" resp="CBETA" type="mod">方【大】，方而【乙】</note><app n="0032036"><lem wit="【大】">方</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">方而</rdg></app>作是念言。法門無邊誓願<note n="0032037" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">學＝覺【乙】</note><note n="0032037" resp="CBETA" type="mod">學【大】，覺【乙】</note><app n="0032037"><lem wit="【大】">學</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">覺</rdg></app>。是
<lb n="0032c16" ed="T"/>願妙觀察智之因也。即智慧門。為大法王故。
<lb n="0032c17" ed="T"/>作是願禮者。乃至成佛當得觀自在菩薩加
<lb n="0032c18" ed="T"/>持。智慧圓滿。</p>
<lb n="0032c19" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0032c1901">次禮北方而作是<note n="0032038" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔念〕－【甲】【乙】</note><note n="0032038" resp="CBETA" type="mod">念【大】，〔－〕【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0032038"><lem wit="【大】">念</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>言。如來無邊誓願仕。是
<lb n="0032c20" ed="T"/>成所作智之因也。即作業門。於諸佛前作諸
<lb n="0032c21" ed="T"/>事業故。若作是願禮者。乃至成佛當得金剛
<lb n="0032c22" ed="T"/>業菩薩加持。於一切佛世界成就廣大供養
<lb n="0032c23" ed="T"/>業。</p>
<lb n="0032c24" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0032c2401">次禮毘盧遮那如來而作是言。無上菩提誓
<lb n="0032c25" ed="T"/>願證。是法界<note n="0032039" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔體〕－【乙】</note><note n="0032039" resp="CBETA" type="mod">體【大】，〔－〕【乙】</note><app n="0032039"><lem wit="【大】">體</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>性智之因也。證大日普賢
<lb n="0032c26" ed="T"/>位。周遍法界。更利眾生故發此願。時十方諸
<lb n="0032c27" ed="T"/>佛同時證明。讚言善哉。是故一切菩薩聖眾
<lb n="0032c28" ed="T"/>皆共守護。不久當得被無上道。總願既說。餘
<lb n="0032c29" ed="T"/>諸別願隨意應陳。乃至以<note n="0032040" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">此＝是【乙】</note><note n="0032040" resp="CBETA" type="mod">此【大】，是【乙】</note><app n="0032040"><lem wit="【大】">此</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">是</rdg></app>善根迴向自他
<pb n="0033a" xml:id="T21.1204.0033a" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0033a01" ed="T"/>平等利益。兼不食不淨之物。心無憂愁不起
<lb n="0033a02" ed="T"/>貪瞋癡等煩惱。不樂世樂深修禪定。如是行
<lb n="0033a03" ed="T"/>者是世大<note n="0033001" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">樂＝藥【甲】【乙】</note><note n="0033001" resp="CBETA" type="mod">樂【大】，藥【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0033001"><lem wit="【大】">樂</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】">藥</rdg></app>。是眾生師。三摩地現前。速證
<lb n="0033a04" ed="T"/>無上正等菩提。</p>
<lb n="0033a05" ed="T"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="close"><cb:jhead><note n="0033002" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（（聖無…品））十六字＝（（不動尊八大童子法一卷））十字【甲】，（（不動尊八大童子法））八字【乙】</note><note n="0033002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（聖無…品）十六字【大】，不動尊八大童子法一卷【甲】，不動尊八大童子法【乙】</note><app cb:word-count="16" n="0033002"><lem wit="【大】">聖無動尊一字出生八大童子祕要法品</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">不動尊八大童子法一卷</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">不動尊八大童子法</rdg></app></cb:jhead></cb:juan></cb:div>
<lb n="0033a06" ed="T"/><cb:div type="w"><p xml:id="pT21p0033a0601"><note n="0033003" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">以下甲本乙本俱無之，乙本奧書曰建久二年十二月四日亥時許於通智院燈下一見了成賢金剛佛子成賢本</note>享保二十龍飛乙卯清明念八日。竊點師
<lb n="0033a07" ed="T"/>傳刊行焉。而無異本可以校者。則以其未
<lb n="0033a08" ed="T"/>正冠書之。以備後人之取捨。冀為訂之。</p>
<lb n="0033a09" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0033a0901">　　　日域豐山長谷輪下桑門無等識</p></cb:div>
